              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25435748/" class="">绪论　关于社会经济转轨国际比较的若干问题</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/30772746/" class=" " title="蚂蚁">蚂蚁</a>
              
